{"tid":772589,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"古圖爾斯：車路士拿八千萬買一個防守球員太瘋狂了","createTime":"2018-08-09T01:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T01:52:53.000Z","uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1d269924d8e5a46ab646717cb28189b35967f84b","tid":772589,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:39:40.000Z","msg":"2018年8月9日，《體育圖片報》消息，古圖爾斯在接受天空體育採訪時表示：車路士拿8000萬買一個防守球員，只能證明現在的轉會市場太瘋狂了。<br />\n<br />\n在剛剛過去的一天，車路士激活了畢爾包門將阿列沙巴拿加8000萬歐元的違約金，創造了門將歷史轉會費紀錄。同時古圖爾斯轉會皇馬的交易完成。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，只剩下一年合同的古圖爾斯為了順利轉會，在世界杯後始終不回到球隊訓練，大玩失蹤。原本希望留住古圖爾斯的車路士不得不拿出巨資購買另一位門將。"},{"pid":"1e57e475f68ae7f9eeb6edf94a29a267b88fd596","tid":772589,"uid":6242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"卡吐好撚憎轟?"},{"pid":"92f28486cd9f126c6fb399ef5d09fb35a3741dac","tid":772589,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"風涼到"},{"pid":"a3e3cff3976ae927705f28efbd28ec9b86ad9b13","tid":772589,"uid":117187,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:45:31.000Z","msg":"唔係你條契弟轉會窗就閂先嗌走洗撚八千萬買個龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6507ac0904f1dd65d40d80f0c527c1ce40ffb63d","tid":772589,"uid":101507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:45:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372c919d4388f5e745ae160f948451f5ffd716a2","tid":772589,"uid":44982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"fake"},{"pid":"94560a9f27dc6786063f94cef59ea6963f89b5db","tid":772589,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"以為9up報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e362e046efe8144c8af6128926630acdf04162","tid":772589,"uid":4444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e3cff3976ae927705